y.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"922a3a9aaad6665a0a35228b3ca4db72fb9d2fce","tid":1385830,"uid":260050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:40:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d4eabb12d713b9fae67d4916a7719058edd6be8b","tid":1385830,"uid":254645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:40:21.000Z","msg":"個頭盔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57842fadf03d2c723fd365ef7d761e00e1089f92","tid":1385830,"uid":1080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:41:04.000Z","msg":"對答得體 有禮大方"},{"pid":"859295052e258ff202998c2a535876bd5fb2ef58","tid":1385830,"uid":177219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:41:46.000Z","msg":"5大訴求！"},{"pid":"514d65e88795568a1c3d75c9ccdfae31ca6d544d","tid":1385830,"uid":290883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:41:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"88d82fce67c23081407c1b7c9ad13ea84c12777e","tid":1385830,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:47:07.000Z","msg":"消防<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24f53edc2a2dbb186242cb46e1a6e22cdcdfceaf","tid":1385830,"uid":164932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:47:27.000Z","msg":"消防救護先係真正既紀律部隊 真正係為市民服務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f1934e4eab8bda22b675daebfd2a0f6a228b1c0","tid":1385830,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:49:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/ass